      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you on the pilferage/error thing, but it's weirdly hard to pin down. we check the cameras and the logs, and everything looks normal. it's like the items are just gone without any obvious movement or security breach. \n\nis there anything else that could explain these tiny, almost \"phantom\" losses? i'm trying to think if there's any weird edge case in warehouse logic or logistics that causes items to just drop off the radar like this.",
